title: The Portfolios of Ansel Adams (Photo Art Ebook).pdf
description:
pdf / English / 1977 / 136 pag / 21 MB

I became interested in Ansel Adams a long time ago when I began to appreciate photography. I fell in love with this book when I first saw it but wasn't able to buy it. Some time later, I made the effort and did purchase the book. I still look through it from time to time, and each time I am as enthralled as I was when I first saw its pages.
The book contains many images that are popular from the Adams archives, and others that should be more popular. I recommend it greatly to those who already appreciate Ansel Adams work, and those who are about to.
